distribution_pattern: distributed in CA, FL and WA.
reason_for_recall: Traditional flavor of Native Catch Salmon Bacon product is recalled because it has the potential to be contaminated with Clostridium botulinum.  The potential for contamination was noted after a routine Washington State Department of Agriculture (WSDA) inspection discovered that the product had potentially been under processed.
initial_firm_notification: Two or more of the following: Email, Fax, Letter, Press Release, Telephone, Visit
product_description: Native Catch Salmon Bacon, Traditional flavor.  UPC 7 83583 27965 9.     Traditional Salmon Bacon is ground and seasoned skinless/boneless salmon, extruded, peppered, smoked, cooled and vacuum packed in 8 oz., 14 oz., and 5 lbs. clear vacuum bags.  Label states keep refrigerated or frozen".
product_quantity: 66/8 oz. pkgs, 372/14 oz. pkgs, 3/5 lb. pkgs;
